casebody.data:
State of FLORIDA, plaintiff,
v.
State of GEORGIA. No. 142, Original. Supreme Court of the United States March 21, 2016.

Motion of Special Master for allowance of fees and disbursements is granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $41,564.31 for the period September 1, 2015, through January 31, 2016, to be paid equally by the parties.
